urdu transliteration text:
Aaj Kabre Mustafa Par Ek Hujoome Aam Hey
Aa Gayi Zainab Madine – Me Bapa Kohram Hey
@HujjatELC

Naam Parke Laash Bete,
Ki Dikhaa Kar Bole Shaah, Ye Hey Sughra Ki Tamanna, Iska Akber Naam Hey
@HujjatELC

Kehtithi Fizza Chini Jaati Hey Zainab Ki Ridaa Ya Ali Aawo Madad Kar – Na Tumhara Kaam Hey
WHILE ZAINAB’S (SA) VEIL WAS BEING SNATCHED, FIZZA (SA) BEGAN CRYING OUT,
@HujjatELC

Kerbala Ke Waki Eko, Ek Muddat Ho Gayee,
Sayyede Sajjad (as) Ki Aankho Me Phir Bhi Shaam Hai
@HujjatELC

Zainab (sa) -e-Muztar Ke Ek Dil, Par Bahattar Daag Hai, Hazir-e-Darbar Hona, Maut Ka Paigham Hai
ON THE HEART OF LADY ZAINAB (SA), SEVENTY-TWO SCARS REMAIN
@HujjatELC
